PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of Jean C. McCloskey, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Canada Development Investment Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term ending March 18, 1995, in the place of Michel Caron, who has resigned.
